\ls1\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	
\f3 \uc0\u8259 
\f0 	}The word and character count will disappear and you will see a pop-up menu appear on the right of the footer view saying \'93General Text\'94 (this just means that the currently selected text isn\'92t recognised as a part of a screenplay).\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1120\li720\fi-720\sl264\slmult1\sa360\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
