\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Try selecting different elements from the pop-up menu on the right of the footer view.\
\pard\tx560\sl264\slmult1\sa360\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 The above text is automatically reformatted to the script element you select each time.\
You can switch between script elements using the tab and enter keys:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\li720\fi-720\sl264\slmult1\sa360\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Hitting enter at the end of the line will take you to the next element.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Hitting tab at the beginning of the line will toggle between different elements.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For some elements, hitting tab at the end of a line will take you to a different element on the next line from hitting enter. For other elements, hitting tab might insert characters.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\li1440\fi-1440\sl264\slmult1\sa360\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	
\f3 \uc0\u8259 
\f0 	}For example, hitting tab at the end of a dialogue line will move to a parenthetical line, whereas hitting tab in a scene heading line will insert a hyphen, ready for you to type the location.\
\pard\tx560\sl264\slmult1\sa360\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 The footer view updates to show what will happen if you press the tab or enter keys (which will move you to the next script element).\
\pard\tx720\sl264\slmult1\sa360\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
